Auguste  Rodin,  patasɩʊ yɑʊ se René François Rodin, palʊlaɩ-ɩ [[Paarii]] kɛ [[kamɩŋ fenaɣ]] kɩyakʊ hɩʊ nɛ naalɛ ŋkʊ wiye kɛ pɩnaɣ 1840 taa, nɛ ɛsɩ Mɛndɔŋ kɛ [[kamɩŋ fenaɣ]] taa kɛ kɩyakʊ hiu nɛ lʊbɛ ŋgʊ wiye kɛ pinaɣ 1917 taa. Ɛkɛ saɣyaɣ taa saɣyʊ sɔsɔ kɛ anasaayɩnaa tɛ waɣ 14 kɛnɛ kɛtɛ hɛkʊ nɛ hɛhʊ alɩwaatʊ taa, nɛ pamaazɩ se ɛnʊ kɛna saɣtʊ kɩfatʊ caa. Palʊlaɩ-ɩ hɔʊ kibaŋʊ taa [[kamɩŋ fenaɣ]] kɩyakʊ hiʊ nɛ naalɛ kɛ pɩnaɣ 1840 taa kɛ Arbalɛtɩ habɩyɛ naadozo nɖɛ yɔɔ, kɛ Paarii egeetiye kagbanzɩ nɖɛ taa, ɛsɩ Mɛndɔŋ kɛ [[kamɩŋ fenaɣ]] taa kɛ kɩyakʊ hiu nɛ lʊbɛ kɛ pɩnaɣ 1917 taa. Ɛ-caa payaɣ size Yohanɛɛsɩ. Ɛkɛ Nɔrmandɩ ɛyʊ. 

