Ɛ-caɣ Paarii tɛtʊ taa pɩnaɣ 1830 taa, nɛ ɛlakɩ anasaayɩ nesi tɛɛ tʊmɩyɛ kɛ fulɩsɩnaa tʊmɩyɛ taa.Ɛ-ɖoo payaɣ se Marie Cheffer, ɛɛkɛ lorrainɩ tʊ. Ɛ-caa tɛ nesi ɖɔkʊ kanaɣ nɛ Gabrielle Cateneau, ɛwɛnɛ-ɩ halʊpʊwa payakɛ se Clothilde nɛ tʊkaɣ nakɛyɛ wɛ pɛhɛkʊ taa panɛ pʊwa ŋka pɛhɛkʊ taa, kɛ alʊwatʊ ndʊ Yohanɛɛsɩ tasɩ nesi ɖɔkʊ yɔ. Auguste tasɩ wɛnaʊ kanaɣ pʊwa kɛ halʊpʊwa payaɣ kaka size se Marie. Ɛ-wɛɛna ɛsɛ kʊdoŋ nɛ ɛ-tapɩziɣ anasaayɩ sʊkʊlɩ labʊ. Ɛlɛ ɛsɔlɩ lɩzɩʊ anjaʊnaa ɛtakayasɩ yɔ, Ɛñɩma na mpʊlɛ powona-ɩ paɖʊ-ɩ anjaʊnaa liziʊ nɛ agoŋta labʊ sʊkʊlɩ, mpʊlɛ ɛwɛna pɩŋzɩ hiʊ nɛ naanza. 

[[File:Buenos Aires-Plaza Congreso-Pensador de Rodin.jpg|thumb|Buenos Aires-Plaza Congreso-Pensador de Rodin]]

Ɖeɖe nɛ sɔnɔ yɔ sʊkʊlɩ ŋgʊ kɩpɩsa sʊkʊlɩ sɔsɔʊ. pʊkɔma pɩnaɣ1855 taa lɛ ɛnɛ Antoine-Louis Barye nɛ Albert-Ernest Carrier-Belleuse paañɩɩnɩ nɛ pokuli saɣtʊ tʊmɩyɛ yɔ. Pɩkpaʊ nɛ mbʊ yɔ ɛpazɩɣ wobʊ paaɖoye sɩʊkpelesɩ kuduyuu taa nɛ ɛlɩzɩɣ doo caanaʊ wondu.

